original_text: Neither did Ephraim drive out the Canaanites that dwelt in Gezer; but the Canaanites dwelt in Gezer among them.
korean_text: 에브라임이 게셀에 거주하는 가나안 족속을 쫓아내지 못하매 가나안 족속이 게셀에서 그들 중에 거주하였더라

sentences.original_text: Neither did Ephraim drive out the Canaanites
but the Canaanites dwelt in Gezer
